      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant restoration or can serve as a comprehensive parts car. The exterior displays heavy wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable rust bubbling on the wheel arches, and a dull finish on the hood. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for a persistent oil leak and a suspension that feels quite loose. Inside, the upholstery is torn in several places and the electronics are intermittent. This is a project car for someone with the time and tools to bring it back to life.",
