    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order, making it a reliable choice for daily driving. The interior is clean and free of major stains or tears, though you might find some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, but there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Overall, it\u2019s a dependable, attractive car that offers great value without the premium price of a brand-new model.",
      "price": 34000.0,
