    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration pros! This vehicle is the perfect candidate for your next big project. While it's currently in poor condition and will require a fair amount of mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back to its former glory, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone with the right skills. Grab this diamond in the rough at a great price and start your rebuilding journey today!",
